dct_description_sm: Shows west German border from 1919 Treaty of Versailles, Territory of Saar, and French-occupied zone in the Rhine Valley.
Includes 3 insets: Corse -- Algerie et Tunisie -- Colonies Francais (w/ 16 micromaps)
Numbered "reference no. 122" in upper margin and 7543, 328 in bottom margin.
